Voidface WASM/WebGPU runtime — placeholder.

This directory holds an ONNX Runtime Web build (`voidface.ort`) and a
tiny TypeScript wrapper for the browser demo. The `.ort` file is a
converted, mobile-quantized version of `../onnx/voidface.onnx`.

See `../../Documentation/deployment/onnx.md` for the export path.
